text:
Dinner here. Food Okok. The bowl use to choose your item is dirty. Chilli didn’t replenish. But when informed the operator, very quickly they top up.
Also didn’t ask whether want Ampang style. When I asked them why my thick beehoon has no thick sauce. Then she told me I never tell I want Ampang style.

Really rude! Why did she put my food on the dirty table with people's leftovers? Even if I  late to pick it up, you can just put it on your stall,why threw my food? She really rude! She even told me to eat the food she just threw !!
